  "title": "Application Processing Officer - Contract Role",
  "description": "<ul><li>Work Location - Central Region</li><li>Working Hours - Mon to Thurs 8.30am - 6pm, Fri 8.30am - 5.30pm</li><li>Monthly Salary - up to $4000 per month</li><li>3 Months Contract (extendable), govt agencies</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assess incoming applications for completeness and compliance</li><li>Identify missing information and maintain accurate application records</li><li>Communicate with applicants to clarify requirements and provide updates</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams and stakeholders during the review process</li><li>Notify applicants of outcomes and process follow-up documentation for successful applications</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in finance, Admin or a related</li><li>2–3 years admin experience, preferably in application processing or customer service</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and database system</li><li>Strong communication, organisational skills, attention to detail</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, kindly email your resume to: <strong>zuli.ng@tg-hr.com</strong></p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
